    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/3dbad523ee018d17e37ad926dbe26953.poster.avif?t=1772373497\" width=614 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/3dbad523ee018d17e37ad926dbe26953.webm?t=1772373497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/3dbad523ee018d17e37ad926dbe26953.mp4?t=1772373497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《红眼露比》是一款黑暗奇幻风格的 Boss Rush 动作游戏。<br>强调特殊核心机制－「专注」，通过专注找出敌人的弱点并给予致命的攻击。<br><br>玩家扮演从斯卡雷特王城逃出来的公主－露比，踏上一场复仇并夺回王国的旅程。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/8f77a61c21f51537ab6b9966e76d8904.poster.avif?t=1772373497\" width=615 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/8f77a61c21f51537ab6b9966e76d8904.webm?t=1772373497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与血污之物决一死战</h2>露比的刀刃无法轻易地伤害到他们，唯有找寻其弱点，给予致命的攻击，才能杀出一条活路。。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/46db7a9030286393cd64de5abd39c551.poster.avif?t=1772373497\" width=640 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/46db7a9030286393cd64de5abd39c551.webm?t=1772373497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >纯血是祝福，亦或是诅咒</h2>为了夺回斯卡雷特王国，露比将要面对各式各样血污之物，古老的神秘教派、不死寄生体、瘟疫根源，握紧刀刃挑战一个比一个更危险的存在。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/faa184095862c5f82b4fea2c047afd72.poster.avif?t=1772373497\" width=640 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/faa184095862c5f82b4fea2c047afd72.webm?t=1772373497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精致像素场景</h2>进入到美丽的像素场景，让每一场危险的战斗中，都能感受到斯卡雷特王国凄美与悲壮。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/1ec7a182c96b25922a83c865550eb4e2.poster.avif?t=1772373497\" width=640 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/1ec7a182c96b25922a83c865550eb4e2.webm?t=1772373497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >吸收纯血，打造护符</h2>每当杀死血污之物，就能吸收他们的力量，提升能力挑战下一场战斗、制造各式各样的护符，打造属于你的战斗风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/17fd2d05847a0e704324425a3f7a1572.poster.avif?t=1772373497\" width=615 height=355 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/17fd2d05847a0e704324425a3f7a1572.webm?t=1772373497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/a0346373cd66a1b4da6540783bca4095.apng?t=1772373497\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845250/extras/a0346373cd66a1b4da6540783bca4095.poster.avif?t=1772373497\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=130 /></picture></span>",
